Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要走這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面容易打滑 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶宗吾 這飄著的石頭是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許和那個環有關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好神奇的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該不知道這個 但覺得很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走這條路真能行嗎 莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 應該是吧哞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:25.91,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,650)\blur5\pos(500,1060)}深淵{\1cBCE347}的{\1cFFFFFF}祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:01:00.61,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}眩しい光が土を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:06.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　そのたねは十分に芽を伸ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:17.12,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}冷たい雨にも　強い風にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:21.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何者でも揺るがない魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕らの背を押すわけはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　くじけそうになった日もあっただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:33.42,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不思議な力あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:40.15,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愛の指す方へ　駆け出す少年のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:44.97,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}長い冬越え　僕ら包む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.34,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春の息吹　福音になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:53.74,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕は君を探し求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:58.19,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}この日をずっと待ち続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:02.54,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じることの強さをそれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それはいつかの孤独を癒すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:13.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あぁ　もしも君が星に帰れと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:18.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいたねをまこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:01:00.61,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}耀眼的光芒照亮大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:06.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}含苞之種由此茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:17.12,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是冰冷的雨水  還是強勁的烈風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:21.53,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這是誰都無法動搖的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.91,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}助我們一臂之力的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.63,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}曾經也有灰心喪氣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:33.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不可思議的力量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:40.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}朝著愛的方向奔跑吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:44.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}跨越長冬  將我們包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.34,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春天的氣息  成為福音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:53.74,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:58.19,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一直等待今天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:02.54,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}堅信著信任這一強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.95,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不久它便會治癒你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:13.00,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果你將回歸繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:18.03,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}去播撒新的種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉這麼紅 不是發燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這是 搞啥 不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 羅曼 還是一起走好些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你臉真的好紅 果然是不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發燒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一碰到宗吾 就覺得燙燙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡跳得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這病呀 估計不會害人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不遠的將來 你肯定會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙的車？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是深淵祭壇？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成沒錯哞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話真能信？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終點就在眼前 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等羅曼 天開始黑了 現在下山崖太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天先休息 明早再出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成 腳好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本沒走路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蜂來電
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發來我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙他…死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找奧托查了下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它煎一下喝掉能退燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒弄給你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒著嗎 花音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這麼正式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面沒準會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 沒有任何安全保障
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花音 你我的婚約解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你尊重自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這會兒了才說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼也别總為了家 和真正喜歡的人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我真正喜歡的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能平安回去 我打算正式向你求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到這了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多虧了宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我的本事 是因為有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最重要的 是菲莉雅努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 石頭又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些孩子們 應該不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 從小時候起一直 在找一種叫<紅石頭>的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初覺得菲莉雅應該是線索 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這風景要是呆在靛藍裡 真别想見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白一色的荒野 色彩奇幻的深林和山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有綠洲城鎮 新娘好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也遇到點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我 能與菲莉雅相遇 能有這麼段旅程 真覺得很慶幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不遠的將來 你肯定會懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之後 想跟菲莉雅去一些地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綠色山谷啥的 還都沒去過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我想說宗吾我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 這裡也有長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛 是不是要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 回去再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了還不算完呢 你可别放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭壇肯定在這門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 宗吾 奧托 我們推
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是入口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個遺跡是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是紅色城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺跡在拒絕我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全猜不到哞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於那份力量 等到了補充之時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待這一刻是多麼讓人心焦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今只等其被邀至我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你「利瑪」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼哞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…黑色的…莫拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上 莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉也不知道哞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了菲莉雅在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道哞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 還行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然哞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃天使的守護者 故不會加害於你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然恕吾一問 為何要糾結於區區一個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾是重要的人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 只要你肯救宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 願意聽你的任何要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與吾同行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之目的 僅是得到你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就救你 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事你就…別再管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個星球只有一個天使和一個守護者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那東西究竟…剛才那黑東西究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉也不知道哞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…菲莉雅為什麼那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 維來聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 冷靜的聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要對付的那些…是職業軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來 多蒙說得沒錯 我就是個沒見識的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護菲莉雅這種事 一開始就注定不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是真心話？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在多蒙面前那份覺悟 就這點程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你怎麼說吧 反正已經沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我老實聽話 多蒙也不用死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不如我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的青梅竹馬 是個正義感的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為救自己珍視的人 至今一直挺身努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 最喜歡這個青梅竹馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以宗吾灰頭土臉哭鼻子的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就去救菲莉雅 你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把力量借我一次 莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:22:00.59,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えないで わたしのなかに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:06.17,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生まれたこのあたたかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.68,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}消えないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.44,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:16.56,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あしたを照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:22.57,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいたいと願うこころが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:28.90,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}孤独のはじまりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:37.41,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}それでも抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:42.67,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ひとつになりたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:47.88,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}触れあう手が遠くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:53.88,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ときが来るとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:59.69,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:05.07,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとつのイノチになろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:10.16,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たとえ離れてもいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:15.46,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}きっとまた会えるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.98,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}きっとまた会えるね…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了星球 為了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「彗星．路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,墮落天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來拿上通往冒險的車票哞
